dct_title_s: Compiled map of existing and proposed roads to Yosemite Valley, 1899
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. In upper margin: Yosemite National Park Commission 1899. In lower margin: S. Doc. 155-56-1. From: Report of the Commission on roads in Yosemite National Park, California ... [Washington, 1900]. 56th Congress, 1st session, Senate doc. no. 155.
